{"tid":1163130,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌","createTime":"2019-05-20T09:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T19:50:57.000Z","uid":54451,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6d2bc761b541a24cb3e0a36a85bc4f50b1bdc9","tid":1163130,"uid":54451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:18:43.000Z","msg":"就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"cb790c5e5e5ff8500faf315c28b43659f383b652","tid":1163130,"uid":140450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"跑完步未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71317fe95fffff0b05ff73fbd1f404cb318f2b6","tid":1163130,"uid":54451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cb790c5e5e5ff8500faf315c28b43659f383b652","tid":1163130,"uid":140450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"跑完步未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"今跑了10000米"},{"pid":"ed1be8b82e702660bc15cc6709ccddeab4d706f4","tid":1163130,"uid":138197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f71317fe95fffff0b05ff73fbd1f404cb318f2b6","tid":1163130,"uid":54451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cb790c5e5e5ff8500faf315c28b43659f383b652","tid":1163130,"uid":140450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"跑完步未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"今跑了10000米"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"天氣點"},{"pid":"69f6a6e9c0c3ea1406b0279179f26ab662b360a6","tid":116